        <body>
            <div type="question">
                <p>Describe your family.</p>
                <note type="word-limit">(at least 30 words)</note>
                <label type="level">
                    <span>A1</span>
                </label>
            </div>
            <div type="answer">
                <p>I've one brother and one sister, they are 14 and 4 years old. My mother is 41 years, she works for the communal house of Waterloo and my father is 51 years, he works in a restaurant in Brussel. My parents are separated since 10 years and now, I'm living by my mother. She has a new boyfriend since 5 years. This man has one son of 14 years and we're living in Waterloo. We're the happiest family.</p>
            </div>
            <div type="grading">
                <label corresp="#examiner.1" subtype="writing" type="level">
                    <span>A2</span>
                    <note type="comment"/>
                </label>
                <label corresp="#examiner.2" subtype="writing" type="level">
                    <span>A2</span>
                    <note type="comment">B1 structures. Not really enough text and vocab to judge if it could be B1</note>
                </label>
                <label corresp="#examiner.3" subtype="writing" type="level">
